cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the semantics and analysis of a declarative model for concurrency, which is a typical topic in programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the application of the model to security protocols (cs.SE) and data flow analysis (cs.CR, cs.DS).
